  ('country', 'MX', '[{"code":"es","type":"official","coverage":1},{"code":"en","type":"widely_spoken","coverage":0.5}]'::jsonb, 'Mexico should score Spanish as the official language while giving moderate English credit because the official tourism system serves international travelers in English and major tourism corridors commonly support English-language services.', 'official_spanish_with_tourism_english_override', '[{"kind":"official_tourism","title":"Visit Mexico English portal","url":"https://visitmexico.com/en/","note":"Mexico''s official tourism platform serves destination planning directly in English for international travelers."},{"kind":"official_tourism","title":"Visit Mexico: X-Can","url":"https://visitmexico.com/en/destino/18031/x-can","note":"Official tourism content for destinations in Mexico distinguishes between local indigenous language use and Spanish as the broadly understood default, supporting Spanish-first traveler coverage."}]'::jsonb),
  ('country', 'CZ', '[{"code":"cs","type":"official","coverage":1},{"code":"en","type":"widely_spoken","coverage":0.65}]'::jsonb, 'Czechia should score Czech as the official language while giving meaningful English credit because official tourism guidance says tourists will usually make themselves understood in English and recent national tourism materials explicitly describe Czechia as a place where visitors can get by in English.', 'official_czech_with_high_english_override', '[{"kind":"official_tourism","title":"VisitCzechia: Language","url":"https://www.visitczechia.com/en-us/travel-info/language","note":"Official tourism guidance says the official language is Czech and that tourists will usually make themselves understood in English."},{"kind":"official_tourism","title":"VisitCzechia: Czechia in the Top 15 Best Countries for Digital Nomads","url":"https://www.visitczechia.com/en-us/news/2025/03/n-czechia-in-the-top-15-best-countries-for-digital","note":"Official tourism guidance says visitors can get by with English in Czechia and cites the country''s high level of English proficiency."}]'::jsonb),
  ('country', 'EE', '[{"code":"et","type":"official","coverage":1},{"code":"en","type":"widely_spoken","coverage":0.75}]'::jsonb, 'Estonia should score Estonian as the national language while giving strong English credit because the official tourism system is built extensively in English and major visitor services are routinely delivered in English across the country.', 'official_estonian_with_high_english_override', '[{"kind":"official_tourism","title":"Visit Estonia: About us","url":"https://visitestonia.com/en/about-us","note":"Estonia''s official tourism portal highlights its English-language platform as a central planning tool for foreign visitors."},{"kind":"official_tourism","title":"Visit Estonia: Official Tallinn Sightseeing Tour","url":"https://visitestonia.com/en/official-tallinn-sightseeing-tour","note":"Official tourism listings show core guided experiences being offered in English and several other languages."}]'::jsonb),
  ('country', 'GR', '[{"code":"el","type":"official","coverage":1},{"code":"en","type":"widely_spoken","coverage":0.75}]'::jsonb, 'Greece should score Greek as the official language while giving strong English credit because official tourism guidance says a large majority of people in the tourist industry speak English and that most Greeks have a good command of it.', 'official_greek_with_high_tourism_english_override', '[{"kind":"official_tourism","title":"Visit Greece FAQ","url":"https://www.visitgreece.gr/faq/","note":"Official tourism guidance says Greek is the official language and that a large majority of people in the tourist industry speak English."},{"kind":"official_tourism","title":"Visit Greece brochures","url":"https://www.visitgreece.gr/media-kit/brochures/","note":"The Greek National Tourism Organisation publishes visitor materials widely in English, reflecting strong English support for travelers."}]'::jsonb),
  ('country', 'SI', '[{"code":"sl","type":"official","coverage":1},{"code":"en","type":"widely_spoken","coverage":0.75}]'::jsonb, 'Slovenia should score Slovene as the national language while giving strong English credit because official tourism guidance explicitly says most people in Slovenia speak English.', 'official_slovene_with_high_english_override', '[{"kind":"official_tourism","title":"I Feel Slovenia: Places to go","url":"https://www.slovenia.info/en/places-to-go","note":"Official tourism guidance says that, in addition to Slovenian, most people in Slovenia speak English."},{"kind":"official_tourism","title":"I Feel Slovenia homepage","url":"https://www.slovenia.info/en","note":"The official tourism homepage repeats that most people in Slovenia speak English."}]'::jsonb),
  ('country', 'LT', '[{"code":"lt","type":"official","coverage":1},{"code":"en","type":"widely_spoken","coverage":0.45}]'::jsonb, 'Lithuania should score Lithuanian as the official language while giving moderate English credit because the national tourism platform serves international visitors in English and core visitor infrastructure is built with foreign travelers in mind, even if English comfort is not as strong as in Scandinavia.', 'official_lithuanian_with_moderate_english_override', '[{"kind":"official_tourism","title":"Lithuania Travel English portal","url":"https://lithuania.travel/en-gb/","note":"Lithuania''s official tourism platform serves destination content and planning information in English for international visitors."},{"kind":"reference","title":"Britannica: Lithuania","url":"https://www.britannica.com/place/Lithuania","note":"Britannica identifies Lithuanian as the official language of Lithuania."}]'::jsonb),
  ('country', 'LV', '[{"code":"lv","type":"official","coverage":1},{"code":"en","type":"widely_spoken","coverage":0.45}]'::jsonb, 'Latvia should score Latvian as the official language while giving moderate English credit because national tourism and culture platforms are structured for international travelers in English, even though everyday language use remains primarily Latvian and Russian.', 'official_latvian_with_moderate_english_override', '[{"kind":"official_tourism","title":"Latvia Travel English portal","url":"https://www.latvia.travel/en","note":"Latvia''s official tourism platform serves broad destination planning content in English for international travelers."},{"kind":"reference","title":"Britannica: Latvia","url":"https://www.britannica.com/place/Latvia","note":"Britannica identifies Latvian as the official language of Latvia."}]'::jsonb),
  ('country', 'HR', '[{"code":"hr","type":"official","coverage":1},{"code":"en","type":"widely_spoken","coverage":0.55}]'::jsonb, 'Croatia should score Croatian as the official language while giving meaningful English credit because the national tourism system serves visitors broadly in English and multilingual support is standard across core travel services and accommodation platforms.', 'official_croatian_with_tourism_english_override', '[{"kind":"official_tourism","title":"Croatia.hr accommodation platform","url":"https://accommodation.croatia.hr/en-gb/apartments","note":"Croatia''s official tourism accommodation system is designed for foreign travelers in English and many other languages, supporting broad English usability in the tourism sector."},{"kind":"reference","title":"Britannica: Croatia","url":"https://www.britannica.com/place/Croatia","note":"Britannica identifies Croatian as the official language of Croatia."}]'::jsonb),
  ('country', 'HU', '[{"code":"hu","type":"official","coverage":1},{"code":"en","type":"widely_spoken","coverage":0.5}]'::jsonb, 'Hungary should score Hungarian as the official language while giving moderate English credit because the national tourism agency serves travelers extensively in English and other world languages, even though everyday national use remains Hungarian.', 'official_hungarian_with_tourism_english_override', '[{"kind":"official_tourism","title":"Visit Hungary English portal","url":"https://visithungary.com/en","note":"Hungary''s official tourism portal serves trip-planning and practical information in English and many other languages for international visitors."},{"kind":"official_tourism","title":"Visit Hungary multilingual platform","url":"https://visithungary.com/es/","note":"The national tourism agency operates the same visitor platform across a broad set of foreign languages, supporting meaningful English-oriented travel usability."}]'::jsonb),
  ('country', 'ID', '[{"code":"id","type":"official","coverage":1},{"code":"en","type":"widely_spoken","coverage":0.35}]'::jsonb, 'Indonesia should score Indonesian as the national language while giving moderate English credit because official tourism guidance says English is not widely spoken nationwide but is understood in major cities, tourist destinations, and by many hotel and airline staff.', 'official_indonesian_with_tourism_english_override', '[{"kind":"official_tourism","title":"Indonesia Travel: Language","url":"https://www.indonesia.travel/us/en/general-information/bahasa/","note":"Official tourism guidance says Bahasa Indonesia is the national and official language and that English is understood in major cities and tourist destinations, especially by hotel and airline staff."},{"kind":"reference","title":"Britannica: Indonesia","url":"https://www.britannica.com/place/Indonesia","note":"Britannica identifies Indonesian as the national language of Indonesia."}]'::jsonb),
  ('country', 'MY', '[{"code":"ms","type":"official","coverage":1},{"code":"en","type":"widely_spoken","coverage":0.75}]'::jsonb, 'Malaysia should score Malay as the national language while giving strong English credit because official tourism guidance says English is widely spoken and most Malaysians are multilingual.', 'official_malay_with_high_english_override', '[{"kind":"official_tourism","title":"Malaysia Truly Asia: About Malaysia","url":"https://www.malaysia.travel/explore/about-malaysia","note":"Official tourism guidance says the national language is Bahasa Melayu and that English is widely spoken across Malaysia."},{"kind":"official_tourism","title":"Tourism Malaysia Kuala Lumpur guide: Useful Information","url":"https://ebrochures.malaysia.travel/en/kuala-lumpur/56-67-useful-information/","note":"Tourism Malaysia destination guides teach Malay phrases alongside English and assume broad English usability for international visitors."}]'::jsonb),
  ('country', 'TH', '[{"code":"th","type":"official","coverage":1},{"code":"en","type":"widely_spoken","coverage":0.55}]'::jsonb, 'Thailand should score Thai as the official language while giving meaningful English credit because the Tourism Authority of Thailand explicitly describes English as Thailand''s unofficial second language in major visitor hubs and provides direct tourist support in English.', 'official_thai_with_tourism_english_override', '[{"kind":"official_tourism","title":"Tourism Authority of Thailand: Language & Culture","url":"https://www.tourismthailand.org/Articles/plan-your-trip-language-and-culture","note":"Official tourism guidance says Thai is the official language and that English has become Thailand''s unofficial second language in population centers that host many foreigners."},{"kind":"official_tourism","title":"Tourism Authority of Thailand: TAT Contact Center","url":"https://www.tourismthailand.org/Articles/linetatcontactcenter","note":"The Tourism Authority of Thailand says its traveler contact center provides information in both Thai and English."}]'::jsonb),
  ('country', 'VN', '[{"code":"vi","type":"official","coverage":1},{"code":"en","type":"widely_spoken","coverage":0.4}]'::jsonb, 'Vietnam should score Vietnamese as the national language while giving moderate English credit because the official tourism board serves international visitors in English and has operated dedicated English-language tourism support for travelers.', 'official_vietnamese_with_tourism_english_override', '[{"kind":"official_tourism","title":"Visit Vietnam official tourism website","url":"https://vietnam.travel/","note":"Vietnam''s official tourism board maintains a full English-language visitor portal for international travelers."},{"kind":"official_tourism","title":"Vietnam Tourism: Stay At Home with Vietnam Kit","url":"https://vietnam.travel/vietnam-stay-at-home-kit","note":"Official tourism guidance says Vietnam set up an English-language tourism helpline for travelers remaining in the country."},{"kind":"reference","title":"Britannica: Vietnam","url":"https://www.britannica.com/place/Vietnam","note":"Britannica identifies Vietnamese as the national language of Vietnam."}]'::jsonb),
  ('country', 'RW', '[{"code":"rw","type":"official","coverage":1},{"code":"en","type":"official","coverage":0.75},{"code":"fr","type":"official","coverage":0.45}]'::jsonb, 'Rwanda should recognize Kinyarwanda as the everyday national language while also giving strong credit to English and some credit to French because official tourism guidance highlights all three as visitor-relevant languages.', 'official_kinyarwanda_with_english_and_french_override', '[{"kind":"official_tourism","title":"Visit Rwanda: Useful Information","url":"https://www.visitrwanda.com/planning/useful-information/","note":"Official tourism guidance says Kinyarwanda, English, French, and Kiswahili are spoken in Rwanda."},{"kind":"government_reference","title":"Rwanda Basic Education Board","url":"https://www.reb.rw/home/language-policy","note":"Government education guidance treats Kinyarwanda, English, French, and Kiswahili as Rwanda''s official languages, while Kinyarwanda remains the unifying national language."}]'::jsonb),
  ('country', 'TZ', '[{"code":"sw","type":"official","coverage":1},{"code":"en","type":"widely_spoken","coverage":0.45}]'::jsonb, 'Tanzania should score Swahili as the national language while giving moderate English credit because English remains important in tourism, safaris, and official visitor-facing services even though daily life is overwhelmingly Swahili.', 'official_swahili_with_tourism_english_override', '[{"kind":"official_tourism","title":"Tanzania Tourism: Destination overview","url":"https://www.tanzaniatourism.go.tz/en/destination/tanzania-unforgettable","note":"Official tourism guidance is structured entirely for international English-speaking visitors, supporting meaningful English usability in the tourism sector."},{"kind":"reference","title":"Britannica: Tanzania","url":"https://www.britannica.com/place/Tanzania","note":"Britannica identifies Swahili and English as the official languages of Tanzania, with Swahili as the national language."}]'::jsonb),
  ('country', 'ZA', '[{"code":"en","type":"official","coverage":1},{"code":"zu","type":"official","coverage":0.7},{"code":"xh","type":"official","coverage":0.6},{"code":"af","type":"official","coverage":0.6},{"code":"st","type":"official","coverage":0.4},{"code":"tn","type":"official","coverage":0.4},{"code":"ts","type":"official","coverage":0.3},{"code":"ve","type":"official","coverage":0.2},{"code":"nr","type":"official","coverage":0.2},{"code":"ss","type":"official","coverage":0.2}]'::jsonb, 'South Africa should recognize its multiple official languages while giving English very strong practical credit because official tourism and travel systems operate heavily in English and it functions as the default cross-group language for many travelers.', 'multiofficial_language_with_english_default_override', '[{"kind":"official_tourism","title":"South African Tourism: FAQ","url":"https://www.southafrica.net/gl/en/travel/article/frequently-asked-questions","note":"Official tourism guidance says South Africa has 11 official languages and that English is widely spoken, especially in tourism and cities."},{"kind":"government_reference","title":"South African Government: Official languages","url":"https://www.gov.za/about-sa/south-africas-people","note":"Government guidance lists South Africa''s official languages and supports English as one of the main intergroup public languages."}]'::jsonb),
  ('country', 'CO', '[{"code":"es","type":"official","coverage":1},{"code":"en","type":"widely_spoken","coverage":0.45}]'::jsonb, 'Colombia should score Spanish as the official language while giving moderate English credit because the national tourism platform serves a broad international audience in English and other languages and visitor-facing guide materials are produced in English.', 'official_spanish_with_tourism_english_override', '[{"kind":"official_tourism","title":"Colombia Travel English portal","url":"https://colombia.travel/en","note":"Colombia''s official tourism platform serves country information, travel guidance, and destination content in English and several other world languages."},{"kind":"official_tourism","title":"Illustrated Handbook for Nature Tourism Guides in Colombia","url":"https://guianaturaleza.colombia.travel/en/","note":"Official tourism guide materials are published in English for international visitors and guides."}]'::jsonb),
  ('country', 'PE', '[{"code":"es","type":"official","coverage":1},{"code":"en","type":"widely_spoken","coverage":0.45}]'::jsonb, 'Peru should score Spanish as the dominant national language while giving moderate English credit because the national tourism system provides official tourist information and assistance in English and many packaged visitor services are explicitly offered in English.', 'official_spanish_with_tourism_english_override', '[{"kind":"official_tourism","title":"iPerú tourist information and assistance","url":"https://www.peru.travel/lafinalenlima/iperu.html","note":"Peru''s official tourism system offers dedicated tourist information and assistance for visitors, including foreign-language support."},{"kind":"official_tourism","title":"Peru Travel package example","url":"https://www.peru.travel/lima2019/complemento/paquetes/paquete32_en.pdf","note":"Official Peru tourism packages explicitly list English-language guide support for international travelers."}]'::jsonb),
  ('country', 'UY', '[{"code":"es","type":"official","coverage":1},{"code":"en","type":"widely_spoken","coverage":0.4}]'::jsonb, 'Uruguay should score Spanish as the official language while giving moderate English credit because the national tourism ministry maintains an English visitor platform and presents destinations directly to international travelers in English.', 'official_spanish_with_tourism_english_override', '[{"kind":"official_tourism","title":"Uruguay Natural English portal","url":"https://uruguaynatural.com/en/","note":"Uruguay''s Ministry of Tourism operates an English-language portal for international visitors."},{"kind":"official_tourism","title":"Uruguay Natural destination content","url":"https://uruguaynatural.com/en/places/colonia/","note":"The national tourism ministry publishes destination information directly in English for foreign travelers."}]'::jsonb),
  ('country', 'FJ', '[{"code":"en","type":"official","coverage":1},{"code":"fj","type":"official","coverage":0.75},{"code":"hif","type":"official","coverage":0.65}]'::jsonb, 'Fiji should give full credit to English because it functions as the main official and traveler-facing language, while also recognizing Fijian and Fiji Hindi as major national languages used widely in daily life.', 'multilingual_country_with_english_default_override', '[{"kind":"official_tourism","title":"Tourism Fiji: Need to know","url":"https://www.fiji.travel/international/need-to-know","note":"Official tourism guidance says Fiji has three official languages, English, Fijian, and Fiji Hindi."},{"kind":"reference","title":"Britannica: Fiji","url":"https://www.britannica.com/place/Fiji-island-country-Pacific-Ocean","note":"Britannica describes English as an official language alongside Fijian and Hindustani varieties."}]'::jsonb),
  ('country', 'GH', '[{"code":"en","type":"official","coverage":1},{"code":"ak","type":"widely_spoken","coverage":0.55}]'::jsonb, 'Ghana should score English as the main national and traveler-facing language. Akan and other Ghanaian languages remain important in daily life, but English is the safest country-level traveler default.', 'official_english_with_local_language_note_override', '[{"kind":"official_tourism","title":"Visit Ghana official portal","url":"https://visitghana.com/","note":"Ghana''s official tourism platform serves international visitors directly in English, supporting English as the main travel language."},{"kind":"reference","title":"Britannica: Ghana","url":"https://www.britannica.com/place/Ghana/Languages","note":"Britannica identifies English as the official language of Ghana and notes Akan as the largest language group."}]'::jsonb),
  ('country', 'MV', '[{"code":"dv","type":"official","coverage":1},{"code":"en","type":"widely_spoken","coverage":0.8}]'::jsonb, 'The Maldives should score Dhivehi as the official language while giving strong English credit because the tourism economy is explicitly international and official visitor systems operate broadly in English.', 'official_dhivehi_with_high_tourism_english_override', '[{"kind":"official_tourism","title":"Visit Maldives official portal","url":"https://visitmaldives.com/en","note":"The Maldives'' official tourism authority serves all practical visitor information in English for international travelers."},{"kind":"reference","title":"Britannica: Maldives","url":"https://www.britannica.com/place/Maldives","note":"Britannica identifies Dhivehi as the official language of the Maldives."}]'::jsonb)
